      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of the exterior finish and interior appointments remains unblemished, reflecting a history of meticulous climate-controlled storage and rigorous maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade specimen that performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory. We invite discerning collectors to inspect this peerless example of engineering excellence.",
