    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines showroom quality. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its original high-gloss finish with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. The interior remains in time-capsule condition, featuring supple leather with no bolster wear and all original factory mats. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, and I have the complete binder of records to prove it. Mechanically silent and cosmetically flawless, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector who demands a vehicle with no stories and no excuses. Inspections are welcome; the quality speaks for itself.",
      "price": 45800.0,
